fields.name: The "pb" command
fields.value:
``` z/pb all/list

-> Gets all of zodisp's PBs through history.`````` z/pb current <version>

-> Gets zodsp's current PB.`````` z/pb new/add <version> <time>

-> Appends a new PB, where <version> is the game version you played on and <time> is the time to be added to the list. Only Zodi can use this command.`````` z/pb remove/removelast

-> Removes the last entry in the PBs list.```
